column1: Hello, this is PECO, the largest pet media in Japan! We love your video and we've sent you an email regarding an opportunity. Please have a look at it. Thank you

Need to be able to give this more thumbs up.  One doesn't do it justice!  Play it again, Henry Mancini. :)

One kitty’s wrong lead is another kitty’s counter- canter. I do wish that kitty would keep his heels down! Lovely video, Emma.  Merry Christmas to you and yours.
